A rough time of seventy hours was put into this simple map.
The purpose was more of an artistic map, some areas are sloppy however, it is in alpha stages.

Everything is fully functional as of now, things will just improve with time when I release beta.
Sorry about the lack of good screenshots, those only show the dull parts of the map.

By the way, this IS my first map, so be gentle.
(I'm really not kidding.)
and god does this look better ingame. These screenshots are terrible.
